pull_request.title: feat: add DataCamp workspace to the overview
pull_request.body:
Hi Robert, 

My name is Filip Schouwenaars, and I lead the development of DataCamp Workspace.
We're building Workspace since 2022, mostly to help our learners apply their data science skills.
I figured it'd be useful to be featured on the list of notebook tools that you put together (thanks for that!).
I took the liberty of adding Workspace to `topNotebookToolOrder` since we have pretty wide adoption and are JupyterLab-compatible, but I'd understand it if you see that differently.

Thanks for considering my PR.

Cheers,

Filip
